node.text:
Today, 79 years ago, the first prototype of the AS 42 was built. While derived from the AB 41 armored car it ironically had no armor itself. About 200 were built and could be equipped with various main armaments such as anti-aircraft cannons, anti-tank rifles, and machine guns.
_________________________________________

node.text:

👉 https://wt.link/battle_of_britain_2021
